  <preparation>Mix together rub ingredients and coat tri-tip, using multipe passes if necessary.  Juices will be drawn into the rub a bit so time is your friend here.

The sauce should be combined in a pot and brought to a boil before simmering for fifteen minutes.  Split batch and use half for grilling mop and half for service.  Baste roast every five minutes through process.</preparation>
